        <abstract>
            <p>At work on abstract.</p>
            <p>Continues argument on effectiveness of dispersal. Has doubts about relationship of isolation to highness of Australian flora. Questions about survival of European plants introduced in Australia.</p>
            <p>CD receives the Wollaston Medal of the Geological Society.</p>
